msgid "Cleanup behavior"
msgstr "Hành Vi Dọn Dẹp"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../files.rst:205
msgid ""
"Starting a **new project** or opening an **existing project** clears the "
"temporary ``.openshot_qt`` working folders so you begin with a clean slate. "
"Your saved projects are not affected, and any assets previously copied into "
